==Awards and statistics==
===Best player awards===

*Best [[Goaltender]]: {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Pekka Rinne]]
*Best [[Defenceman]]: {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Juuso Hietanen]]
*Best [[Forward (ice hockey)|Forward]]: {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Oscar Möller]]

===All-star team===
*Goaltender: {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Pekka Rinne]]
*Defence: {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Anton Belov]], {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Juuso Hietanen]]
*Forwards: {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Petri Kontiola]], {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Oscar Möller]], {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Viktor Tikhonov (ice hockey, born 1988)|Viktor Tikhonov]]
*[[Most valuable player|MVP]]: {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Pekka Rinne]]

